Class JarGenrule

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BuildEngineAction, HasOutputName, AllowsNonAnnotatedFields, HasMultipleOutputs, SupportsInputBasedRuleKey, BuildRule, HasNameAndType, BinaryBuildRule, Comparable<BuildRule>

    public final class JarGenrule
extends BaseGenrule<GenruleBuildable>
implements BinaryBuildRule
    A rule similar to Genrule except specialized to produce a jar.

    The produced jar behaves similarly to a jar produced by java_binary, which means it can be executed by buck run or using the $(exe ) macro.
